headline: General Dynamics (GD): Assessing Valuation After Jet Ramp-Up, New Defense Deals and Analyst Upgrades
summary: General Dynamics (GD) has been on investors radar after tightening up its Aerospace operations and leaning into fresh demand for its G700 and G800 jets, while also landing sizable new defense work. See our latest analysis for General Dynamics. All of this has underpinned a solid run in the stock, with the latest share price at $336.41 and a strong year to date share price return of 28.89 percent.
